- `restoreOuterMouse()` — re-enable if was disabled.

**`session/tmux/winsize_unix.go`** (build tag `!windows`):
- `monitorWindowSize()` — SIGWINCH listener, debounce (50ms), two goroutines, respect `t.ctx.Done()`.

